{"tid":401009,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解內房股會升？","createTime":"2017-09-15T09:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T13:46:31.000Z","uid":122516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"028e1efe240b295109326d9fe13df888bc8a5195","tid":401009,"uid":122516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:33:19.000Z","msg":"求解答"},{"pid":"ecf41967d19e18ecf168a00e78bf6351a7f974da","tid":401009,"uid":57308,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:35:49.000Z","msg":"花旗发表研究报告，称国统局公布了8月经济数据，该行认为楼市数据与其他宏观指标相比表现强劲，且高于市场的审慎预期。即使8月仍是传统淡季，物业销售价值及销量仍同比分别升6.4%及4.3%，按月则分别升3.5%及4.3%。<br />\n<br />\n该行预期在高基数的情况下，物业销售同比升势将缓和，但由于行业首八个月销售及投资表现强劲，相信全年销售表现将好过预期。<br />\n<br />\n花旗认为内房行业2017至2019年将处于&ldquo;超级盈利周期&rdquo;，加上去杠杆、销量增长动力强劲、以及估值吸引，重申对内房股正面看法。<br />\n<br />\n行业中，该行首选碧桂园(02007)、龙湖(00960)、金茂(00817)、富力(02777)、合景泰富(01813)  及旭辉(00884)。"},{"pid":"463cbda443184e00385f6390691a7a745fe4da28","tid":401009,"uid":122516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:28:05.000Z","msg":"你都無解釋我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfaf4cebcfc3ef127ebb33b7a33854734016acf4","tid":401009,"uid":2127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:28:44.000Z","msg":"人民幣升"},{"pid":"e4582e54491528b3db6e9b0f9e9ca4429e8a52cb","tid":401009,"uid":136727,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/202940_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F202940_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9e9fa7d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9bbb0473a4a963ad4d50cf91ae6d93fc1b65876","tid":401009,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:30:20.000Z","msg":"點解我隻1321日跌夜跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p